{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1dd59d2521","title":"关于荆制佑工作安排的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0b031fa43a","index":0,"year":1951,"month":9,"day":8,"articleId":"1dd59d2521"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"14d52cc00f","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"荆铜佑，曾留学日本，任过李宗仁的顾问、湖南省制宪会议主席。当时闲居在家，1951年后任湖南省文史馆馆员。"},{"id":"06f0930a72","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"程颂云，即程潜，当时任中央人民政府委员、中南军政委员会副主席。程星龄，当时任湖南省人民政府副主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"fe5c56178f","type":"title","text":"关于荆鼠佑\"工作安排的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521"},{"id":"14d52cc00f","type":"paragraph","text":"道衡同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521"},{"id":"06f0930a72","type":"paragraph","text":"荆制佑一信付上，请察阅。其中所述淑浦乡间对荆不尊重的事，请予查明的办。荆在辛玄革命后曾当我们学校的英文教员，四十年来他做过些什么事，是否和国民党反动派有过关系，我完全不明了，请你向程颂云、程星龄请人及沉陵地委问明，并决定是否帮助他在长沙解决工作问题。至于他要求去日本的事，现在没有此种可能。此致敬礼","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521"},{"id":"d1eca074c9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521"},{"id":"0a2590322b","type":"paragraph","text":"九月八日荆先生：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521"},{"id":"588f349d4c","type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十二日惠书敬悉。所述乡间情况，值得注意，已将来信转给中共湖南省委查明办理。先生出外工作一事，也要湖南省委药情帮助。如先生有兴趣，可与湖南省委统一战线部部长刘道衡先生通讯商的。此复","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521"},{"id":"c09bd1e4b0","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521"},{"id":"e51fbcc1e3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521"},{"id":"43afa325f2","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年九月八日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521"}],"page":{"id":"d199702a9f","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1dd59d2521","start":490,"end":491}}}},"__N_SSG":true}